Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.001\fs75\c&H0521D2&\3c&HEAE9C3&\4c&H38B04E&\bord5\shad8\pos(760,870)\fad(900,0)}Here Comes the High Collar Lady
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.59,0:00:13.80,Default,,0,0,20,,Did you hear about it?{Have you heard the gossip already?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.80,0:00:17.96,Default,,0,0,20,,And have you seen it?{And have you made sure yourself with those eyes?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.96,0:00:22.21,Default,,0,0,20,,Those two shockingly beautiful eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.21,0:00:27.52,Default,,0,0,20,,Overflowing with startling romance{A shockingly overflowing romance}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:29.73,Default,,0,0,20,,All-consuming{The hottest topic now}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:31.90,Default,,0,0,20,,Inescapable{It's all about this}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:36.31,Default,,0,0,20,,With a Taishō Era charming lady
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.31,0:00:40.70,Default,,0,0,20,,Hi, Hi, Hi, High Collar Lady's coming
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.70,0:00:45.07,Default,,0,0,20,,With her gentle heart, winning everyone over
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.07,0:00:49.46,Default,,0,0,20,,Hi, Hi, Hi, High Collar Lady's coming
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.46,0:00:53.84,Default,,0,0,20,,With her gentle heart, winning everyone over
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.84,0:00:58.09,Default,,0,0,20,,Hi, Hi, Hi,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.09,0:01:02.47,Default,,0,0,20,,Hi, Hi, Hi, High Collar Lady's coming
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.47,0:01:06.81,Default,,0,0,20,,With her gentle heart, winning everyone over
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.00,0:01:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio didn't come home after school, \Nso the Ijuuins were understandably worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.81,0:01:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Concerned for her safety, \NShinobu went to look for her personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.14,0:01:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.13,0:01:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio's father stopped him in his tracks, demanding an explanation of his relationship with Kichiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.71,0:01:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.96,0:01:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,through listening to Kichiji's life story, \NBenio realized how caring Shinobu really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.73,0:01:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And now she's gushing with joy, ecstatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.59,0:01:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But the world is smaller than we think,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.91,0:01:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and the unlikable Lieutenant Colonel​ Innen \Nruns into them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.70,0:02:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet another humiliation at the hands of Benio only serves to throw more fuel into the fire of his vendetta,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.31,0:02:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,which now roars with a ferocious strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.15,0:02:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Still unaware of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.10,0:02:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,for how long will our High Collar Lady \Nbe able to retain that carefree smile of hers?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.51,0:02:18.89,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,500)\c&HF5E1DD&\blur1.001\bord0\b1\pos(720,150)} Episode 23 \N {\fs90} Heaven Yesterday, Hell Today
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.74,0:02:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hammers mark the city rhythm: \Nwhack, whack, whack!{same song from ep 3, 9:32}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.98,0:02:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Streetcars scurrying about...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.18,0:02:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.73,0:02:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, we wouldn't want anyone \Nto see you in this state.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.06,0:02:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry to your room, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.31,0:02:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, what's the buzz?\NLet's drink some more!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.28,0:02:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.36,0:02:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on, Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.77,0:02:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be a killjoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.10,0:02:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,To learn that Shinobu's is not a playboy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.22,0:02:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And on top of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.63,0:02:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I know that you're going to be the one with the Young Master, I should be glad to give up on him. {ref: ep 22, 16:29}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.93,0:02:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Didja hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.87,0:02:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She said it!{don't really understand what she's saying}{same}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.35,0:03:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.85,0:03:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Ranmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.83,0:03:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Lady Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.81,0:03:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.71,0:03:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!\NOh no! We've been spotted!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.13,0:03:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What a disgraceful look!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy! And I love everyone in this house!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.02,0:03:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{skip}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.07,0:03:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So many nice people in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.73,0:03:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And I love my dear Kisaragi, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.19,0:03:27.32,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H34A1E1&\an2\fs20\frz335.4\t(100,700,\fs200)\move(774,669,-211,-207,700,1200)} Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Benio, that's a bit too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.83,0:03:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers to this beautiful life in the pink!{don't really understand what she's saying; same}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.56,0:03:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.01,0:04:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My favorite person in the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.64,0:04:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to see you in high spirits, Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.44,0:04:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Shinobu is right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.04,0:04:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you wearing nothing but pajamas? {maybe "pajamas" because this kimono doesn't exactly have the same ring as underwear in western sense}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.13,0:04:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanted to set the mood, \Nyou'd be better off wearing a negligee. {probs meaning "to press me [for sex]", semaru isn't really "to provoke" as in "to feint"}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you're just messing around...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.74,0:04:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nobody's messing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.43,0:04:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, \Nwhat are you even reading this late?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A Russian-Japanese dictionary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Russian? Russian...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.38,0:04:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Russian. Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.55,0:04:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You know there's been \Na revolution in Russia, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Emperor Nicholas II was overthrown,\Nand now they're in a protracted civil war.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.99,0:04:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes... Kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.35,0:04:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So the USA and Japan are considering an intervention \Nto quell the insurrectionists.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me... \NYou're going to Russia?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.55,0:04:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.77,0:04:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt they'll dispatch the troops stationed in Tokyo, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.18,0:05:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Geographically, it makes more sense to dispatch the Kyushu and Hokuriku garrisons there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.93,0:05:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.73,0:05:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.36,0:05:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.59,0:05:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you love me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.60,0:05:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.69,0:05:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.84,0:05:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world did I just say?\NIt seems the alcohol went straight to my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.59,0:05:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I do love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha... Even if I am a careless, average girl, \Nwho goes berserk when drunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.70,0:05:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Shut up, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.54,0:05:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{skip}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.09,0:05:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He is so close to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.31,0:05:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He is getting even closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.56,0:05:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.72,0:05:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, good night then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.84,0:05:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.70,0:06:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she didn't understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.11,0:06:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I just confessed my love, yet she was completely unmoved...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.58,0:06:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, I'll lose all of my confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.82,0:06:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel weird, like I've just been told \Nsomething important...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.75,0:06:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, Benio! \NYou still haven't changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't remember what he said...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.79,0:06:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.60,0:06:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! She has a terrible fever! This is serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.77,0:06:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody, please!\NSomebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange, huh?\NI still can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.53,0:06:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?\NWhat might have happened to Lady Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,She's never had a fever before...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.56,0:06:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How could such a healthy girl develop a fever?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe something happened \Nthat shook her to the core. {/shocked}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be it, \Nsomething we don't know about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.50,0:06:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.06,0:07:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I slept so well! \NAh, it feels great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That reminds me, \Njust what happened yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.69,0:07:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's been helping me in any way he could, \Nand was there when I needed encouragement.{\i0}{ep22 15:43}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He is a truly caring and chivalrous man.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.87,0:07:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your marriage will be the one \Nthat stands the test of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I remember now!\NYesterday was an amazing day!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.54,0:07:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.98,0:07:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And alley-oop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.71,0:07:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Lady Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.71,0:07:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.37,0:07:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a second there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.20,0:07:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. These silk stockings are for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.37,0:07:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, so wonderful! \NIs this for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.96,0:07:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time, nylon wasn't invented yet
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.94,0:08:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and wearing silk stockings was every girl's dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever, while we're at it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.45,0:08:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have these too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.41,0:08:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? You're so kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.44,0:08:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.92,0:08:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.61,0:08:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Benio, you look rather happy this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.67,0:08:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something good happen to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.55,0:08:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Countess, please find\Nsomewhere to put these on display.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.18,0:08:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, thank you, Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.12,0:08:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, what's this "good thing" that happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm, you see... Actually, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.44,0:08:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,wanted to express my utmost gratitude to both of you for raising Shinobu to be the lovely person he is today. {maybe "surrounded by your love"}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.41,0:08:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.98,0:08:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all because I raised him right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.41,0:08:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Yet it seemed to me like you barely did any raising.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.45,0:08:55.75,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.91,0:08:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, would you look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.37,0:09:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It laid an egg!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.78,0:09:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My, congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.30,0:09:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, hurry up with laying some of your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.76,0:09:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Eggs?! {maybe a wordplay too, like tama = balls}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.63,0:09:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, my bad. Not eggs,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.72,0:09:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,great-grandchildren! {tamago = egg, himago = great-grandchild}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.43,0:09:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A new spring is about to come to our home!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The spring I've been awaiting for all my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:10:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up, Ushigorou. I want to stop by my old home before school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! But are ya sure we have the time, Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.01,0:10:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a big deal if I'm late by just a few minutes. {nc whats goji there}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.46,0:10:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Lord, Young Lady is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.88,0:10:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What? Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.80,0:10:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Benio, what did they kick you out for this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.25,0:10:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, cut it out! I came this morning \Nto tell you some good news for a change!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.41,0:10:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it. \NWhat really happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.80,0:10:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.68,0:10:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to extend my thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Benio, where did that come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.43,0:11:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You've always told me how Shinobu
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.00,0:11:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,is a truly noble person \Nand that I should trust him unquestionably.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, I can finally say\Nthat I'm convinced of his greatness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.21,0:11:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I express my admiration for your keen eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.13,0:11:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.30,0:11:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So I take it that things \Nare finally going well with the lieutenant?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.45,0:11:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.68,0:11:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.25,0:11:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm late for school!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.60,0:11:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She never changes, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But aren't you glad that she now stands firmly \Non track to marriage?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.70,0:11:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear, you can rejoice now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.08,0:11:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that Benio \Nis finally at peace with her destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.24,0:11:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Praise be the Lord, praise be the Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.97,0:12:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The year is 1918 - Japan is on the verge of a historic decision to dispatch troops to Siberia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.85,0:12:09.77,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(758,222)\bord0\blur1.4\fade(400,400)\fs160\b0\c&HEFE6EC&\fnSegoe Print}July 1918 {大正七年七月}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.21,0:12:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop... Turn right! \NStart marching!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Second Lieutenant Ijuuin Shinobu coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Second Lieutenant Ijuuin, uh-huh,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.17,0:12:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,there are orders for your transfer, uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.82,0:12:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Transfer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.61,0:12:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.95,0:13:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Imperial Army Second Lieutenant Ijuuin Shinobu,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,As of today, you are seconded to the 12th Army Division, 14th Infantry Regiment, 3rd Battalion,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.41,0:13:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,as a field commander of the 2nd Platoon, uh-uhm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.83,0:13:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yessir!\NWhere is 12th Division stationed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.49,0:13:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Kokura in Kyushu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.85,0:13:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyushu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A long way from here...\NBut why this sudden reassignment?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Within the next week, \Nyou need to finish your work
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.81,0:13:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and depart for your new post. Uhm, hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yessir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.34,0:13:36.76,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(900,1900)\c&H483F2A&\3c&HB5A57F&}Atonashi School for Girls
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.87,0:13:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,First you obey your husband, \Nthen you obey your son,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.19,0:13:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the only correct path \Na Japanese woman can take.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.69,0:13:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.03,0:13:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.78,0:13:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.67,0:14:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,My apologies!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.24,0:14:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha-Ha-Hanamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.83,0:14:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, I got you, \NStanding in the hallway isn't half-bad either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.11,0:14:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up!\NBow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.36,0:14:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be here all day long!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.24,0:14:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.49,0:14:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.78,0:14:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, she's gone now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.64,0:14:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh, she's so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.90,0:14:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You provoked the teacher again, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.72,0:14:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I just wanted to share \Na bit of my happiness with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.57,0:14:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Did they appoint the date \Nfor your marriage?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.88,0:14:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Benio, what was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.26,0:14:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty close, but not quite it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.66,0:14:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing, Benio!\NCongratulations!{Tamaki's voice only}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.92,0:14:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy for you! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.04,0:14:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.52,0:14:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, by the way, girls, how about you come to the Ijuuins' place this afternoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:15:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm holding a small party to celebrate\Nand you're all invited!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.99,0:15:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, so you're getting married soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.98,0:15:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!\NBe sure to come, all of you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.48,0:15:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that noise? {nc}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.42,0:15:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, I can't see well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.25,0:15:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope it's not infectious.{don't really understand what she's saying - same}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.03,0:15:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, so they're transferring you to Kyushu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.58,0:15:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds hella sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.68,0:15:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.27,0:15:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.37,0:15:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Colonel​ Innen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Heard you're going to Kokura, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.89,0:15:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear the guys there are having a hard time \Nscrambling the expeditionary force, {guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.06,0:15:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,so you better get used to dealing with rural roughnecks, \Nnot well-behaved Tokyoites. {same}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.53,0:15:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how long will our noble boy last?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.52,0:15:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Will, I'll be going. \NWatch yourself, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.24,0:15:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That was snide of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.28,0:15:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand him at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.38,0:16:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lieutenant Colonel​ Innen is well-connected in the Army High Command, so please keep your guard up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.47,0:16:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.64,0:16:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That self-important mop-head...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.98,0:16:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Out of sight - out of mind - \Nthat is my priority. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.33,0:16:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can you imagine how will that schoolgirl react...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sublieutenant Ijuuin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.98,0:16:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Major Hanamura, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.15,0:16:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.04,0:16:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true that you're being transferred to Kokura?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yessir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one getting transferred \Nin our entire division. {to Kokura }
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.69,0:16:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no other personnel changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.97,0:16:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But the division commander \Nreceived an official order...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.04,0:16:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Just when Benio finally came \Nwith some good news this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.73,0:16:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.89,0:17:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Major, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.44,0:17:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Father{idk how these two lines could play out in English}, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.28,0:17:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You've just called me "Father," haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.24,0:17:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This is wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.29,0:17:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, how many people \Nwould probably be coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.95,0:17:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you can place it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.74,0:17:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.36,0:17:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All of my classmates have enormous appetites,\Nso make sure to prepare lots of refreshments, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.62,0:17:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.58,0:17:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio, there is a call for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.46,0:17:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.29,0:17:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, it's Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.21,0:17:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Transferred?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.97,0:17:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Benio!\NHey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.94,0:17:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.70,0:17:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going away...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.16,0:17:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu is going away...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.23,0:17:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.18,0:17:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Simply ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.27,0:18:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're being transferred!{\i0}{/he's being transferred}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.93,0:18:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're being transferred!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.70,0:18:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're being transferred...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.34,0:18:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How did it come to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They're sending him so far away...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.54,0:18:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Shinobu told me just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.67,0:18:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Get yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.40,0:18:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay... But dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.44,0:18:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for the country... \NOur country!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.20,0:18:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going away...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.17,0:18:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu is going...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.28,0:18:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...far, far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.20,0:18:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you heard the news? \NShinobu's getting transferred!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.35,0:18:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.64,0:18:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This means the odds look good for me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.92,0:19:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.40,0:19:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? O-Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.73,0:19:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How cruel! Didn't you say yourself \Nthat you don't want to see his face anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, yes, I did that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.67,0:19:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that my hand moved on its own!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.83,0:19:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Silly hand! Silly! You must not do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.89,0:19:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how it could have happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.15,0:19:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio, your friends have come \Nto party with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.92,0:19:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.72,0:19:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.83,0:19:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We took you up on that offer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.34,0:19:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, show us your future husband \Nand the love nest you've prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.66,0:19:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We wanna hear all the cheesy stories you got!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.23,0:19:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a little something from us to celebrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not much, but I'll prepare something better \Nfor your actual wedding ceremony!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.55,0:19:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, accept our presents, Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.26,0:19:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. These are all great presents...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.95,0:20:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I can't have them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.11,0:20:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.79,0:20:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't look at Benio, \Nshe's so pitiable!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.59,0:20:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen, Ranmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.37,0:20:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Shinobu...\NThey're transferring him to faraway Kyushu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.42,0:20:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.09,0:20:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a call for you, Lady Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.60,0:20:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, it's Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.85,0:20:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Benio? Have you heard \Nabout Shinobu getting transferred?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.54,0:20:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.70,0:20:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Something about that doesn't feel right to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.70,0:20:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't feel right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.96,0:20:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be that you did something \Nto incur the wrath of Lieutenant Colonel​ Innen?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.95,0:20:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Colonel​ Innen?\NI don't quite remember... Innen...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.30,0:21:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.62,0:21:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Soldiers this, soldiers that - \Nit's nuffin' to be proud of, you! {ref: ep 17, 22:03}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.96,0:21:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Actually, Father, could it be that this Lieutenant Colonel​ Innen has...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.28,0:21:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Face the shape of an upside-down onion,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.84,0:21:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,lifeless eyes with a sinister look in them,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.80,0:21:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,lips the shape of the Mt. Fuji,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.41,0:21:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,a stupid mustache
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.90,0:21:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and to top it off, eyebrows that look \Nlike a line of dots - is that him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.33,0:21:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How harsh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.82,0:21:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to know that descriptive powers \Nrun in the family. {not sure what he means, what's it to do with benio being his child?}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.80,0:21:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he does have a face like that, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.38,0:21:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.63,0:21:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this mean that it was he \Nwho masterminded Shinobu's transfer out of spite?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.55,0:21:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm, well, I can't \Nrule this possibility out...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.89,0:21:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, given the circumstances, \Nwe'll have to postpone the wedding...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.69,0:21:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what you should be saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.89,0:21:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio! What are you going to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.10,0:22:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up! Hold up I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.52,0:22:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all so sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.37,0:22:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even know \Nwhat I should put in his suitcase.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.41,0:22:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a shame...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.02,0:22:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lady Benio!{あら紅緒様}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.79,0:22:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you headed?{どこへいらっしゃるの}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.24,0:22:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I am now going to meet \NLieutenant Colonel​ Innen of 1st Division.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.89,0:22:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Things have taken a turn for the worse:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.46,0:22:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,yesterday was heaven, but today has become hell, \Nand she needs to let that anger out somehow. {guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.84,0:22:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Our High Collar Lady is armed and dangerous and she's willing to put her life on the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.67,0:22:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,High Collar Lady isn't having any more of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.90,0:23:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Even as a single woman, she's not afraid \Nto take on the entire 1st Division of the Imperial Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.31,0:23:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a real emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.17,0:23:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,News spread like wildfire - \Nfrom the Count to the servants,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.05,0:23:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,to the geisha Kichiji, \Nthe Violet Band from Kanto family,{from ep 14}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.07,0:23:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,even Benio's teacher and classmates
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.88,0:23:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,enter the great coalition to help Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.06,0:23:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,See in the next episode of {\i1}Here Comes the High Collar Lady:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.15,0:23:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"I Can't Stand Martinets!" {陸軍さん許せない!} {/Army men cannot be forgiven}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.27,0:23:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.53,0:23:34.78,Default,,0,0,20,,How are you feeling? I am Benio
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.04,0:23:41.57,Default,,0,0,20,,Please call me High Collar Lady, \Nbecause I'm in that phase
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.50,0:23:48.49,Default,,0,0,20,,When it's getting so hard \Nto be honest with the people I love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.72,0:23:57.31,Default,,0,0,20,,I just want to know what's in his heart;\N I want him to turn around before he leaves
